4️⃣ Material Page Route (Concept):- 
:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::

This concept is often used in Flutter, but it’s useful to understand the comparison.

In Flutter:

Navigator.push(
 context,
 MaterialPageRoute(builder: (context) => ProfileScreen()),
);

In React Native navigation, the equivalent is:

navigation.navigate("Profile")

Both mean:

Push a new screen onto the navigation stack

Comparison of Navigation Types:- 
::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::

| Navigation       | Best For                    |
| ---------------- | --------------------------- |
| Stack Navigator  | screen-to-screen navigation |
| Tab Navigator    | bottom navigation bar       |
