2️⃣ Deep Linking:- 
::::::::::::::::::::::::

Deep linking allows users to open a specific screen using a URL.

Example:

myapp://profile/123

This directly opens the profile screen.

Real world examples:

Instagram → instagram.com/user

YouTube → youtube.com/watch?v=123

Why Deep Linking is Important

Deep linking is used for:

Email links
Push notifications
Web links
Marketing campaigns
Basic Deep Linking Setup

Example configuration:

const linking = {
prefixes: ['myapp://'],
config: {
screens: {
Profile: 'profile/:id'
}
}
}

Then pass it to NavigationContainer.

<NavigationContainer linking={linking}>
Example URL
myapp://profile/101

This opens:

ProfileScreen

With parameter:

id = 101

